{"doc":{"isMarkdown":true,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"Cookie","mdn_url":"/zh-CN/docs/Glossary/Cookie","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)","sidebarHTML":"","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p>Cookie 就是访问者在访问网站后留下的一个信息片段。</p>\n<p>Cookie 用于个性化用户的体验。可能包含用户在访问网站时的参数或输入。用户可以自定义浏览器来接受，拒绝或删除 Cookie。</p>\n<p><code>Cookie 可以在服务器级别设置和修改，使用 Set-Cookie</code> <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/HTTP/Cookies\">HTTP header</a>, 或者在 JavaScript 中用 <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Document/cookie\"><code>document.cookie</code></a>.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"了解更多","title":"了解更多","isH3":false,"content":""}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"general_knowledge","title":"General Knowledge","isH3":true,"content":"<ul>\n  <li><a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/HTTP_cookie\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">HTTP cookie</a> on Wikipedia</li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"了解更多","id":"了解更多"}],"summary":"Cookie 就是访问者在访问网站后留下的一个信息片段。","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-10-01T03:41:16.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"Cookie","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"Cookie","locale":"es","native":"Español"},{"title":"Cookie","locale":"fr","native":"Français"},{"title":"Cookie","locale":"ja","native":"日本語"},{"title":"Cookie","locale":"ru","native":"Русский"},{"title":"Cookie","locale":"zh-TW","native":"正體中文 (繁體)"}],"source":{"folder":"zh-cn/glossary/cookie","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/zh-cn/glossary/cookie/index.md","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/921c46a374ab0a9f4cc809af0370f8c412e54701","filename":"index.md"},"parents":[{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Glossary","title":"术语表"},{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Glossary/Cookie","title":"Cookie"}],"pageTitle":"Cookie - 术语表 | MDN","noIndexing":false}}